description=Extend battery lifespan by limiting charging current, temperature, and voltage. Includes AMPS (Find my switch): a universal charge-control finder that detects and verifies the switch that works on your phone, writes only reversible switches, and restores on exit. Systemless; works on any root (Magisk / KernelSU / APatch). Community fork of VR-25's ACC, maintained by seyedehsanhadi. Telegram: https://t.me/+hU1oF-BCf5hmM2Rk
